OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1776059756
OL,3,CCabinet to hold emergency meeting on
OL,4,Csixth day of fuel protests
OL,6,FAn emergency Cabinet meeting has been
OL,7,Fcalled as Ireland's Government
OL,8,Fprepares to sign off on measures it
OL,9,Fhopes will bring protests over fuel
OL,10,Fcosts to an end.
OL,12,FThe protests, which involved blockades
OL,13,Fof Ireland's only oil refinery as well
OL,14,Fas key depots, strangled fuel
OL,15,Fdistribution across the country and
OL,16,Fprompted an escalated policing
OL,17,Fresponse that resulted in several
OL,18,Farrests and public order gardai
OL,19,Fdeployed in Cork and Galway.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
