OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1776059756
OL,3,CCabinet to hold emergency meeting on
OL,4,Csixth day of fuel protests
OL,6,FParticipants ` largely led by
OL,7,Fhauliers, farmers, and agricultural
OL,8,Fworkers ` began separate but
OL,9,Fcoordinated actions on Tuesday with
OL,10,Fslow-moving convoys and outright
OL,11,Fstoppages on major motorways, as well
OL,12,Fas the blockades of critical
OL,13,Finfrastructure.
OL,15,FThe protests rolled into a sixth
OL,16,Fconsecutive day on Sunday, with
OL,17,Fspokesmen calling on Government to
OL,18,Ftake urgent action to reduce fuel
OL,19,Fcosts which they say are at
OL,20,Funsustainable levels and will lead to
OL,21,Fpeople going out of business.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1776059756
OL,3,CCabinet to hold emergency meeting on
OL,4,Csixth day of fuel protests
OL,6,FThe coalition is expected to sign off
OL,7,Fon fuel-cost measures on Sunday, but
OL,8,Fit remains to be seen if it will
OL,9,Fconvince protesters to call off their
OL,10,Factions before the return of schools
OL,11,Fon Monday adds to pressure on the
OL,12,Froads.
OL,14,FThe Irish police service, An Garda
OL,15,FSiochana, cleared a blockade of the
OL,16,FWhitegate oil refinery in Co Cork
OL,17,Faround lunchtime on Saturday and vowed
OL,18,Fto implement further enhanced
OL,19,Fenforcement actions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1776059756
OL,3,CCabinet to hold emergency meeting on
OL,4,Csixth day of fuel protests
OL,6,FIt saw physical clashes between
OL,7,Fprotesters and gardai, who used pepper
OL,8,Fspray during the hour-long operation
OL,9,Fwhich resecured access for fuel trucks.
OL,11,FGardai were later called to a similar
OL,12,Faction at Galway harbour, where
OL,13,Fhundreds of protesters gathered in
OL,14,Fpouring rain while restricting access
OL,15,Fto a fuel depot by blocking the way
OL,16,Fwith tractors.
OL,18,FMembers of the Public Order Unit,
OL,19,Fwearing protective gear and batons,
OL,20,Fwere at the scene for hours overnight.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1776059756
OL,3,CCabinet to hold emergency meeting on
OL,4,Csixth day of fuel protests
OL,6,FGarda Commissioner Justin Kelly had
OL,7,Fvowed to to step up enforcement
OL,8,Fagainst fuel-cost protesters
OL,9,F"endangering the state" by blocking
OL,10,Fcritical infrastructure.
OL,12,FProtesters' demands for meetings with
OL,13,FGovernment were not acceded to but
OL,14,Frelevant ministers held talks with
OL,15,Festablished national representative
OL,16,Fbodies on Friday and Saturday.
OL,18,FThese meetings concluded with a
OL,19,F"substantial" package involving a
OL,20,Ftemporary fuel transport support
OL,21,Fscheme" and "temporary fuel support".
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@WO]{D@AOU{D@MO]}D@GO]}D@MOU}D@
OL,26,AdO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
