PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1776059756
OL,3,CCabinet to hold emergency meeting on
OL,4,Csixth day of fuel protests
OL,6,FIt is understood the transport support
OL,7,Fscheme would see direct payments to
OL,8,Fbusinesses in the sectors affected by
OL,9,Fhigh fuel costs.
OL,11,FA senior source said the scheme will
OL,12,Fbe part of a broader package on the
OL,13,Ffuel crisis.
OL,15,FThe engagements included Irish Road
OL,16,FHaulage Association president Ger
OL,17,FHyland, who said there were "the bones
OL,18,Fof an agreement" with the Government.
OL,26,@yD@]OUzD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1776059756
OL,3,CCabinet to hold emergency meeting on
OL,4,Csixth day of fuel protests
OL,6,FHe added that he hoped the
OL,7,F"substantial package", understood to
OL,8,Finclude a direct payment scheme, would
OL,9,Fbe agreed by Sunday morning.
OL,11,FThe Cabinet is due to meet on Sunday
OL,12,Fafternoon to sign off on the measures.
OL,14,FThe pledge of a "substantial" package
OL,15,Fwas not enough to dissuade protesters
OL,16,Faway from other blockades of a fuel
OL,17,Fdepot in Foynes, Co Limerick and the
OL,18,Fmain thoroughfare of Dublin city
OL,19,Fcentre.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@UO]vD@QOUvD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
