CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1776059756
OL,3,CCabinet to hold emergency meeting on
OL,4,Csixth day of fuel protests
OL,6,FCommissioner Kelly said: "Some people
OL,7,Fhave decided to escalate an already
OL,8,Fdifficult situation by blockading
OL,9,Fcritical national infrastructure such
OL,10,Fas fuel depots and refineries.
OL,12,F"This has resulted in fuel shortages
OL,13,Fthat are directly impacting on
OL,14,Femergency services such as hospitals,
OL,15,Fthe ambulance service and the fire
OL,16,Fservice, as well as businesses and the
OL,17,Fgeneral public.
OL,19,F"These are blockades. They are not a
OL,20,Flegitimate form of protest."
OL,26,@nD@ZOUtD@AOU{D@AOU|D@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
