CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1776059756
OL,3,CCabinet to hold emergency meeting on
OL,4,Csixth day of fuel protests
OL,6,FHe said: "We gave the blockaders fair
OL,7,Fwarning that we were moving to
OL,8,Fenforcement and they choose to ignore
OL,9,Fit and continue to hold the country to
OL,10,Fransom."
OL,12,FA small number of Defence Forces
OL,13,Fpersonnel with heavy-lift recovery
OL,14,Ftrucks have been on standby to assist
OL,15,Fgardai with moving large vehicles if
OL,16,Fneeded.
OL,26,@nD@JOUrD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
