PN,31310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1776059756
OL,3,CCabinet to hold emergency meeting on
OL,4,Csixth day of fuel protests
OL,6,FThe escalated enforcement action came
OL,7,Fafter Fuels for Ireland chief
OL,8,Fexecutive Kevin McPartlan said around
OL,9,F600 of the 1,500 filling stations in
OL,10,Fthe Republic of Ireland had run dry on
OL,11,FSaturday morning.
OL,13,FHe had predicted that the number
OL,14,F"would grow quite dramatically" if the
OL,15,Fblockades on Whitegate in Galway and
OL,16,FFoynes, Co Limerick, continued.
OL,18,FElsewhere, Rosslare Europort was
OL,19,Fexpected to hit capacity by Sunday
OL,20,Fevening or Monday morning.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
