OL,3,CCabinet to hold emergency meeting on
OL,4,Csixth day of fuel protests
OL,6,FOperations at the port, run by Irish
OL,7,FRail, have been affected by a blockade
OL,8,Fof fuel protesters in the nearby town
OL,9,Fof Kilrane, Co Wexford.
OL,11,FA spokesperson for Irish Rail said the
OL,12,Fport will soon be unable to take in
OL,13,Fany more freight ` resulting in ships
OL,14,Fhaving to wait on anchor or being
OL,15,Fdiverted to another port if possible.
OL,17,FBlockades have resulted in full
OL,18,Fclosures of parts of the M50 ring road
OL,19,Faround Dublin, as well as other major
OL,20,Fmotorways.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
