FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1776059756
OL,3,CCabinet to hold emergency meeting on
OL,4,Csixth day of fuel protests
OL,6,FMeanwhile, police in Northern Ireland
OL,7,Fsaid they were "maintaining an ongoing
OL,8,Fassessment" in relation to social
OL,9,Fmedia posts calling for similar
OL,10,Fplanned protests there.
OL,12,FA PSNI spokeswoman said: "A policing
OL,13,Fresponse has been prepared, if needed,
OL,14,Fto ensure public safety and to help
OL,15,Fminimise any potential disruption to
OL,16,Fthe wider community."
OL,26,@oD@POUpD@KO]tD@ZOUxD@UO]
